1
00:01:41,720 --> 00:01:42,680
Go find someone.

2
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:08,400
Aya.

3
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:10,039
Don't blame me

4
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,800
for making the decision for you.

5
00:02:13,440 --> 00:02:14,480
In this world,

6
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:16,860
I'm the only one you can trust.

7
00:02:19,920 --> 00:02:20,520
Did you find them?

8
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,000
No.

9
00:02:21,440 --> 00:02:22,240
Keep looking.

10
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:12,800
Let's go.

11
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,560
Once I get rid of them,

12
00:03:40,320 --> 00:03:41,579
I'll come back for you.

13
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:44,600
Don't blame me for using someone else to kill him.

14
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:45,760
He dug his own grave.

15
00:03:59,240 --> 00:03:59,770
Let's go.

16
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,680
Long time no see.

17
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:36,080
(in Thai) Over there!

18
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:38,640
Hurry up!

19
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:16,000
Urine-soaked mop! Zhang Fei's roar!

20
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:16,760
Come on!

21
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:29,840
Liu Yu.

22
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:36,920
Take this back!

23
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:40,760
Come on!

24
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:42,680
After them!

25
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:56,500
Come on, quick!

26
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,740
Close the door, quick!

27
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,720
Is this the girl?

28
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:39,200
You were used.

29
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:50,000
Am I dead?

30
00:06:52,159 --> 00:06:53,600
You must be an angel.

31
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:01,520
You look just like someone I know.
